%20into%20the%20trip%2C%20the%20deal%20flow%20found%20him%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20founder%20he'd%20been%20getting%20to%20know%20over%20eight%20months%20texted%20to%20say%20he%20was%20kicking%20off%20a%20raise.%20Other%20investors%20were%20circling%2C%20but%20the%20founder%20wanted%20Das%20and%20his%20firm%2C%20Menlo%20Ventures%2C%20at%20the%20table.%20So%20between%20temple%20visits%20and%20kaiseki%20meals%20%E2%80%94%20and%20once%20when%20he%20told%20his%20girlfriend%20he%20was%20soaking%20at%20the%20onsen%20%E2%80%94%20Das%20coordinated%20with%20colleagues%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20after%20he%20returned%20to%20California%2C%20the%20founder%20pitched%20Menlo's%20partners.%20That%20evening%2C%20Das%20%E2%80%94%20newly%20engaged%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20founder%20celebrated%20a%20handshake%20agreement%20over%20Japanese%20food%20at%20Ozumo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20only%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20working%20in%20venture%2C%20Das%20has%20quickly%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frising-stars-of-the-venture-capital-industry-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eone%20to%20watch%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20joined%20Menlo%20after%20stints%20as%20an%20engineer%20at%20Facebook%20and%20Google%2C%20and%20as%20an%20early%20employee%20at%20the%20enterprise%20search%20company%20Glean%2C%20where%20he%20helped%20scale%20the%20business%20from%20having%20no%20product%20to%20a%20%242.2%20billion%20valuation.%20In%20June%2C%20that%20figure%20jumped%20to%20%247.2%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Menlo%2C%20he's%20carved%20out%20a%20role%20at%20the%20cutting%20edge%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20enterprise%20software%20investing.%20He%20helped%20launch%20the%20firm's%20%24100%20million%20Anthology%20Fund%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20with%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20earned%20a%20reputation%20for%20his%20unusually%20technical%20diligence.%20Now%2C%20with%20his%20promotion%20to%20partner%2C%20Das%20is%20part%20of%20a%20new%20generation%20climbing%20venture%20capital's%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20talk%20onstage%20in%20a%20brightly%20lit%20workspace.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c47e72f9db348adc0b6af9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeedy%20Das%20and%20Ben%20Mann%3Cp%3EMenlo%20Ventures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20firms%20are%20looking%20to%20leaders%20who%20come%20from%20the%20trenches%20of%20engineering%20and%20startups%2C%20not%20just%20the%20spreadsheet%20jockeys%20groomed%20in%20banking.%20In%20today's%20market%2C%20where%20breakthroughs%20come%20wrapped%20in%20jargon%20and%20white%20papers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftechnical-has-become-paramount-for-young-talent-at-vc-firms-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechnical%20fluency%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20a%20nice-to-have.%20It's%20practically%20the%20job%20description.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMenlo%20is%20bulking%20up%20its%20roster%20with%20investors%20who%20bring%20technical%20bona%20fides.%20This%20year%2C%20it%20hired%20cybersecurity%20guru%20Matt%20Kraning%2C%20who%20sold%20his%20startup%20to%20Palo%20Alto%20Networks%20in%20a%20deal%20topping%20%241%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmenlo-ventures-partner-tim-tully-invests-in-generative-ai-startups-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETim%20Tully%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20general%20partner%20and%20Splunk's%20former%20chief%20tech%20officer%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20founders%20%26quot%3Bwant%20investors%20who%20they%20can%20talk%20shop%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22227c63ec-36ed-494d-a413-62e3c2b3c1a6%5C%22%3EInside%20track%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDeep%20learning%20and%20natural%20language%20processing%20have%20always%20been%20central%20to%20Glean's%20products.%20But%20as%20models%20advanced%20gradually%2C%20then%20all%20at%20once%2C%20CEO%20Arvind%20Jain%20assembled%20a%20dedicated%20%26quot%3Btiger%20team%26quot%3B%20of%20engineers%20to%20fold%20the%20latest%20capabilities%20into%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDas%20led%20that%20effort%2C%20steering%20the%20company%20beyond%20its%20original%20Google-like%20search%20interface%20into%20something%20that%20digests%20data%2C%20interprets%20it%2C%20and%20can%20perform%20tasks%20on%20a%20user's%20behalf.%20Today%2C%20the%20company%20is%20on%20pace%20to%20hit%20%24250%20million%20in%20annualized%20revenue%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20up%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglean-ai-startup-annual-recurring-revenue-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%24100%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20says%20the%20systems%20and%20products%20that%20Das%2C%20who%20left%20Glean%20in%202024%2C%20helped%20create%20are%20%26quot%3Bstill%20central%20to%20how%20our%20customers%20use%20Glean.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20known%20Deedy%20for%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bhis%20impact%20at%20Glean%20was%20significant%20as%20a%20founding%20engineer%20%E2%80%94%20from%20shaping%20our%20products%20and%20raising%20the%20bar%20on%20engineering%20excellence%20to%20mentoring%20teammates%20and%20helping%20build%20the%20culture%20that%20carried%20us%20through%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227285%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20look%20at%20a%20laptop%20computer%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c47da4183847aa39d6b76b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20discerning%20Deedy%20Das%20checks%20out%20a%20product%20demo%20at%20a%20builder%20event%20Menlo%20Ventures%20hosted%20in%20partnership%20with%20Anthropic.%3Cp%3EMenlo%20Ventures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDas%20says%20his%20background%20gave%20him%20an%20early%20read%20on%20OpenRouter%2C%20which%20offers%20developers%20a%20single%20platform%20to%20access%20multiple%20large%20language%20models.%20Having%20built%20a%20version%20of%20the%20same%20tool%20at%20Glean%2C%20he%20knew%20the%20demand%20would%20be%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20met%20founder%20Alex%20Atallah%2C%20Das%20didn't%20hedge%3A%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20absolutely%20going%20to%20be%20useful.%20Model%20velocity%20is%20not%20going%20to%20stop.%20Whenever%20you're%20ready%20to%20raise%2C%20we're%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20He%20laughs%20now%2C%20knowing%20that%20he%20didn't%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20promise%20that%20deal%2C%20but%20was%20willing%20to%20bluff.%20Menlo%20first%20backed%20the%20startup%20with%20a%20modest%20check%20through%20the%20Anthology%20Fund%20before%20doubling%20down%20to%20lead%20the%20%2440%20million%20Series%20A%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Das%20says%20OpenRouter%20has%20scaled%20from%20processing%20about%2010%20trillion%20tokens%20annually%20to%20more%20than%20250%20trillion%20%E2%80%94%20a%2025x%20jump%20in%20throughput.%20Because%20its%20business%20model%20ties%20revenue%20directly%20to%20usage%2C%20that%20surge%20suggests%20revenue%20has%20grown%20in%20lockstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDas's%20other%20investments%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-software-engineer-skills-jobs-ai-cursor-chatgpt-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWispr%20Flow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20app%20that%20turns%20messy%20speech%20into%20polished%20writing%2C%20and%20Goodfire%2C%20a%20research%20lab%20focused%20on%20understanding%20why%20machine%20learning%20models%20behave%20the%20way%20they%20do.%20Both%20came%20in%20through%20the%20Anthology%20Fund%20before%20Menlo%20followed%20on%20with%20more%20capital.%20These%20deals%20and%20others%20earned%20Das%20a%20spot%20on%20Business%20Insider's%202024%20list%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%