ounts%20stay%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEntry-level%20security%20roles%20typically%20start%20in%20the%20%24105%2C000%20base%20salary%20range%2C%20with%20total%20compensation%20higher%20once%20stock%20and%20bonuses%20are%20included.%20If%20you%20would%20like%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstay-at-home-mom-to-6-figure-tech-job-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebreak%20into%20cybersecurity%20yourself%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%20five%20things%20you%20need%20to%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb1ab43f-743e-4f4f-b2eb-74d5878d8556%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Be%20prepared%20for%20the%20day-to-day%20changes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20day-to-day%20always%20looks%20a%20bit%20different%2C%20so%20be%20prepared%20for%20the%20unexpected.%20It%20depends%20on%20the%20activity%20of%20threat%20actors.%20For%20example%2C%20imagine%20it's%20Thanksgiving%20and%20people%20are%20shopping%20online.%20If%20someone%20tries%20to%20steal%20a%20cent%20out%20of%20every%20transaction%2C%20that's%20where%20we%20step%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20task%20is%20to%20put%20out%20that%20fire%3A%20contain%20the%20situation%2C%20remove%20the%20bad%20actors%2C%20and%20ensure%20systems%20are%20running%20smoothly%20again.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20good%20people%20can%20still%20do%20their%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20doctor%20accessing%20patient%20records%20in%20a%20hospital%20%E2%80%94%20without%20being%20hindered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20take%20them%20out%2C%20we%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20alerts%2C%20detections%2C%20and%20monitors%20we%20should%20put%20in%20so%20that%20it%20doesn't%20happen%20again.%20We%20have%20to%20ask%20ourselves%2C%20how%20did%20they%20get%20in%3F%20What%20are%20our%20learnings%20to%20make%20sure%20this%20doesn't%20happen%20again%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250e7942b-323a-4f60-bc5f-0b029487a0cb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Start%20learning%20early%20and%20get%20hands-on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20early%20in%20your%20career%2C%20research%20and%20educate%20yourself%20through%20courses%2C%20lectures%2C%20podcasts%2C%20and%20YouTube%20videos.%20I'd%20highly%20recommend%20checking%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftldrsec.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETLDRSec%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20curates%20excellent%20security%20content.%20Certifications%20can%20also%20be%20a%20helpful%20way%20to%20structure%20your%20learning%20and%20build%20a%20strong%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20you%20can%20also%20get%20hands-on%20experience%20by%20playing%20games.%20Tools%20like%20Capture%20the%20Flag%20exercises%20let%20you%20practice%20in%20a%20gamified%20environment%2C%20exploring%20dummy%20websites%20or%20simulated%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20streamlined%20many%20parts%20of%20cybersecurity%20by%20automating%20detection%20and%20analysis%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20introduced%20new%20risks%20as%20attackers%20use%20it.%20My%20advice%20is%20to%20build%20strong%20fundamentals%20first%20and%20then%20explore%20AI%20tools%20to%20augment%2C%20not%20replace%2C%20your%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-dos-and-donts-tips-advice-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetworking%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20matters.%20Attend%20meetups%2C%20conferences%2C%20and%20internships%20whenever%20possible.%20If%20you've%20demonstrated%20potential%20in%20any%20role%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20people%20in%20the%20field%20%E2%80%94%20connections%20and%20proven%20capability%20can%20open%20doors%2C%20even%20if%20you're%20just%20starting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e045ba64-d28d-44a2-8050-a3378255b41d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20don't%20need%20a%20traditional%20path%20to%20get%20here%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20career%20as%20a%20business%20analyst%20in%20the%20airline%20industry%20and%20then%20moved%20to%20a%20data%20analyst%20role%20for%20anti-money%20laundering.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20moved%20into%20processes%20and%20then%20into%20security%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20as%20a%20cyber%20incident%20responder%20at%20first%20%E2%80%94%20more%20on%20developing%20tools%20in%20cybersecurity.%20I%20eventually%20landed%20in%20an%20incident%20responder%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20specifically%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-into-cybersecurity-career-job-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20into%20cybersecurity%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20I%20just%20knew%20I%20was%20good%20at%20IT%20and%20program%20management%20and%20wanted%20a%20new%20challenge.%20Then%20someone%20trusted%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20would%20you%20like%20to%20join%20our%20organization%20as%20an%20early-career%20security%20person%3F%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20challenging%2C%20but%20focusing%20on%20delivering%20results%20in%20ambiguous%20situations%20is%20what%20got%20me%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20more%20common%20routes%20into%20cybersecurity.%20Someone%20might%20pursue%20a%20degree%20in%20cybersecurity%2C%20computer%20science%2C%20or%20information%20systems%2C%20and%20complement%20it%20with%20courses%20in%20threat%20intelligence%2C%20digital%20forensics%2C%20and%20detection%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ea8db6b-a0c3-4156-8e63-4f902b32b365%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20You%20can%20be%20remote%2C%20but%20community%20helps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20you%20work%20often%20doesn't%20matter%20at%20all.%20Most%20of%20my%20team%20is%20in%20Dublin%2C%20Utah%2C%20or%20a%20small%20town%20in%20the%20UK.%20However%2C%20it%20does%20help%20to%20be%20in%20a%20place%20with%20others%20doing%20the%20same%20job%20as%20you%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20want%20to%20network%20and%20learn%20hands-on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20late%20nights.%20You%20might%20be%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20fire%20working%20till%203%3A00%20a.m.%2C%20and%20in%20those%20cases%2C%20it's%20good%20to%20have%20that%20community%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20coming%20into%20the%20office%20because%20I%20love%20to%20meet%20people%2C%20see%20if%20I%20can%20joke%20a%20little%20bit%20about%20it%2C%20and%20try%20to%20solve%20the%20same%20problem%20together.%20It's%20amazing%20to%20be%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-hybrid-work-from-home-jobs-persisting-fewer-new-roles-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20from%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20sometimes%20it's%20nice%20to%20be%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab4b4d2b-a0da-4a3c-93dc-5dece9c29b18%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20You%20must%20be%20able%20to%20handle%20high-pressure%20environments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20have%20a%20job%20like%20mine%2C%20you%20need%20to%20know%20how%20to%20maintain%20calmness%20in%20a%20room%20full%20of%20chaos.%20It's%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20everyone%20else%20stays%20collected%20and%20does%20their%20job%20because%20the%20moment%20you%20lose%20that%2C%20nothing%20gets%20done.%20That%20ability%20to%20create%20clarity%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20chaos%20isn't%20something%20you%20learn%20in%20college%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20something%20you%20practice%20and%20develop%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20OK%20%E2%80%94%20and%20important%20%E2%80%94%20to%20know%20when%20to%20ask%20for%20help.%20One%20mistake%20people%20make%20is%20that%20they%20don't%20ask%20questions.%20Everyone%20is%20on%20edge%20when%20something%20goes%20wrong%2C%20but%20that's%20exactly%20what%20you%20should%20do.%20Be%20the%20trailblazer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20love%20about%20my%20job%20is%20the%20immediate%20impact.%20You%20might%20think%20to%20yourself%2C%20%3Cem%3EI%20saved%20someone's%20email%20inbox%20from%20being%20hacked%20and%20got%20it%20back%20to%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Although%20it's%20high-pressure%20and%20can%20be%20chaotic%2C%20the%20perk%20is%20that%20you%20get%20to%20see%20the%20impact%20of%20helping%20someone%20right%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-principal-security-engineer-shares-how-get-into-cybersecurity-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757927102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c480f2f9db348adc0b6b7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-principal-security-engineer-shares-how-get-into-cybersecurity-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tannu%20Jiwnani%20started%20her%20career%20as%20a%20business%20analyst%20in%20the%20airline%20industry%20and%20is%20now%20a%20principal%20security%20engineer%20at%20Microsoft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alyshia%20Hull)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-principal-security-engineer-shares-how-get-into-cybersecurity-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manoj%20Bajpayee%20opens%20up%20about%20SRK's%20National%20Award%20win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757926601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123897122%2Cimgsize-53778.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmanoj-bajpayee-addresses-comparisons-opens-up-about-shah-rukh-khans-national-award-win-calls-it-loser-conversation%2Farticleshow%2F123897122.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F123897122.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EManoj%20Bajpayee%20called%20the%20National%20Award%20debate%20with%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20pointless%20and%20said%20it%20should%20be%20left%20in%20the%20past.%20He%20praised%20his%20films%20but%20feels%20awards%20ar